title: The 6 Steps to Hitting Any Goal
itunes:title: The 6 Steps to Hitting Any Goal
description:
Episode 227 - Here I share the 6 step process to setting and achieving any goal that you set for yourself. Whether it's a New Year's Resolution or a big life goal, this goal setting process from Napoleon Hill's Book "Think and Grow Rich" will help you accomplish them.
